node.text: Louisiana's favorite fried fritter gets a savoury spin and a surprise inside. It’s stuffed with braised oxtails cooked in a flavourful stew served for dipping, and topped with a savoury spice mix! Link in bio 🔗

node.text: This dessert pizza is your one-way ticket to the island of Motunui. Set sail across a sweet sea of blue spirulina cream cheese frosting topped with roasted pineapple, white chocolate, macadamia nuts, and orchids and surrounded by toasted coconut sand. Garnish with a heart of Te Fiti cookie. Recipe link in bio 🔗
